hdb.table.column

Class HarambeColumnList

  • java.lang.Object
    • hdb.table.column.HarambeColumnList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColumnList, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Column>

    public class HarambeColumnList
extends java.lang.Object
implements ColumnList
    Main implementation of interface ColumnList for HarambeDB hdb. This class uses a LinkedDict to represent the list of columns. .

    This class is a member of the HarambeDB database framework.

    See Also:
    Column, ColumnList, Serialized Form
